{"tid":1358533,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"7.27 入元朗義士裝備要再升級！","createTime":"2019-07-24T02:57:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T03:21:52.000Z","uid":38465,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1ad5d10db40ab2d72f53a582a039c37b8c7afcc5","tid":1358533,"uid":38465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:57:50.000Z","msg":"（非白色恐佈，無fact checked)<br />\n轉自朋友，話元朗如果7.27個日有人係非指定區域遊行或者衝擊，一律照劈<br />\n<br />\n我唔知真定假，但升級左防具先一定無壞，今次防既係刀具唔係棍同椒，所以做足番護手之類"},{"pid":"cec3c327d541fcae83e6cfa0b3b52745ff3b55c9","tid":1358533,"uid":165246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:58:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請大家一定要記得！！！！<br />\n１。全面撤回逃犯條例<br />\n２。撤銷暴動定性<br />\n３。釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n４。全面實行雙普選<br />\n５。成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任＋徹查警黑勾結元朗站暴打站內市民<br />\n6 。721上環對示威者開36槍 義士被狗開槍擊中 下落不明<br />\n要求公佈義士下落<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"6793db18f9c13513df1d51e64db91e6e31c99c82","tid":1358533,"uid":37081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:59:00.000Z","msg":"要拎埋防身武器 <br />\n唔洗主動打人 俾人打要還手"},{"pid":"5e4f138ec4a35dfc59ee566adeec0bca8bab26c7","tid":1358533,"uid":38465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6793db18f9c13513df1d51e64db91e6e31c99c82","tid":1358533,"uid":37081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:59:00.000Z","msg":"要拎埋防身武器 <br />\n唔洗主動打人 俾人打要還手"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:59:40.000Z","msg":"係！但係驚被狗𢭃"},{"pid":"8ed2892a3c1b83827217fa6a6b376f4588a78e9d","tid":1358533,"uid":38465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:04:23.0